---
title: Baked Jerk Tofu with Coconut Rice and Pineapple Salsa
description: Mild Caribbean Jerk sauce is such a festival of flavours that we had to step up every element of this lively dish. From pineapple-cilantro salsa to sweet coconut rice, each colourful bite is a delight.
